parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to repair or replace defective Takata airbags can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: No symptoms reported
but concerns about the safety of the airbags and the lack of available replacement parts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard near the airbag can cause shrapnel to be propelled towards occupants in the event of an airbag deployment, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Cracking of the dashboard near the passenger side airbag
rattling or vibrating of the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag did not deploy in an accident
concern about the safety of the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard near the passenger airbag can potentially cause shards of plastic to become projectiles in the event of an airbag deployment, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracks appearing on the dashboard
particularly near the passenger airbag
with some owners reporting multiple cracks in different locations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the vehicle to lose power, become stuck in gear, or fail to shift into gear, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the transmission fails to shift into gear
the vehicle becomes stuck in gear
the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate when shifting, which can lead to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The transmission shifts harshly
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting
the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power or failure to shift into gear, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift into gear
the vehicle loses power
the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake and power train issues can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate when braking or accelerating, which can lead to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or hesitates when braking or accelerating
the brake warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the transmission dipstick tube can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power or failure to shift into gear, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission dipstick tube fractures
the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle rollaway can cause accidents or injuries if the vehicle rolls into traffic or pedestrians.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls away without warning
the vehicle is unable to be stopped.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard can lead to a safety concern when the airbag is deployed, potentially causing additional injuries.
symptoms: Cracks in the dashboard
often around the passenger airbag area
exposing parts of the airbag
and potentially affecting airbag functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock can trap occupants inside the vehicle, making it difficult or impossible to exit in an emergency situation.
symptoms: Unlocked driver door will not open from the inside.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Excessive Rust on Truck Frame and Underbody
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive rust on the truck frame and underbody can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents or safety issues.
symptoms: Visible rust on the truck frame and underbody.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Loose and Falling Off Front Bumper Plastic Fog Light Assembly
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loose and falling off front bumper plastic fog light assembly can cause a crash or accident due to falling parts from the car.
symptoms: The front bumper plastic fog light assembly becomes loose and falls off.
